high_descs: Turn around and face the white sink to your left
Pick up the hand wash container next to the tooth brush
Turn around and walk towards the black bin next to the toilet.
Place the container inside the black bin.
Turn around and face the sink.
Walk towards the sink and pick up the container.
Turn around and walk towards the black bin.
Place the container inside the black bin.
anns.task_desc: Place the two hand-wash containers inside the black bin.

high_descs: Turn around and move to the left side of the vanity, to the left of the sink.
Pick up the soap bottle nearest to you.
Turn around and move to the trash bin to the right of the toilet.
Place the soap bottle into the trash bin.
Turn around and move back to the left side of the vanity, to the left of the sink.
Pick up the remaining soap bottle on the vanity.
Turn around and move back to the trash bin to the right of the toilet.
Place this soap bottle in the trash bin as well.
anns.task_desc: Place the two soap bottles on the vanity in the trash bin.

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the wall, then turn right to face the counter.
Pick up the closest bottle of lotion off of the counter.
Turn around and walk over to the small black bin in the corner of the room.
Put the bottle of lotion into the small black bin.
Turn around and walk over to the counter.
Pick up the bottle of lotion off of the counter.
Turn around and walk over to the small black bin to the right of the toilet.
Put the bottle of lotion into the small black bin.
anns.task_desc: Move two bottles of lotion from the counter to a small black bin.
